                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-04-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 21, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Draft of naval instructions forwarded by the dispatch bag to day. Please send
                    names of the United States vessels, and if possible their commanders, designated
                    to police North Pacific Ocean and Bering Sea.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
